Outdoor Photography is for the serious amateur and semi-professional photographer who is passionate about the British countryside and its wildlife. It is the UK’s only photography magazine dedicated exclusively to the coverage of landscape, wildlife and the environment. Each issue features an inspiring array of landscape and wildlife photographs with regular contributions by Britain’s leading photographers. The magazine is also renowned for its field tests of cameras and other relevant equipment plus informed techniques and instruction by leading photographers.
